00:49:18.230 --> 00:49:21.440
So it's always governments using
the lens of national security

00:49:21.440 --> 00:49:24.660
to infringe upon
people's civil liberties.

00:49:24.660 --> 00:49:27.160
And so it is something I think
we should be concerned about.

00:49:27.160 --> 00:49:29.584
And I think the difference
in the US versus China

00:49:29.584 --> 00:49:32.000
is that in the US, there's at
